+# Private Mods to Forte
+
+This is the privately modified version of `Forte` for use in the `Piano` pipeline.
+
+## Version Info
+
+- DATE: 2025-08-07
+- HEAD: 3071d5b
+- VERSION: 1.0.0-411-g3071d5b
+
+## 2025-08-07
+
+### Added
+- **IRIS Cluster Support**: Added new EOS configuration file (`eos.config`) for the IRIS cluster
+  - Added new `eos` profile in `nextflow.config`
+  - Configured executor settings, process resource limits, and parameters
+  - Set up paths, environment variables and singularity options for the `IRIS` cluster
+
+### Changed
+- **Publish Mode**: Updated `nextflow.config` to change `publish_dir_mode` from 'link' to 'copy'
+  - This is needed on IRIS as the work and output directories are on different mount points (`/scratch` vs `/data1`)
\ No newline at end of file
